The paper discusses a chatbot that uses information retrieval and machine learning techniques to answer questions and handle multi-turn conversations. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and computational linguistics (cs.CC). Among these, cs.CL and cs.IR are the most likely categories, as they directly relate to the paper's focus on language understanding and information retrieval.
